ai-patthana16.73:0.2_0: Having given the immaculateness of the Dhamma
ai-patthana16.73:0.3_0: Seeing over motion, wrapped in the mind, and so on.
ai-patthana16.73:1.1_0: Not long afterwards, not consciousness arises in someone whose mind is the wrong way, not longing for the mind, nor is the cause of consciousness.
ai-patthana16.73:1.1_1: This is the section in brief.
ai-patthana16.73:3.1_0: Not long afterwards, not consciousness arises in someone whose mind is the wrong way, not preoccupied with the mind, and whose mind is the cause of condition.
ai-patthana16.73:3.1_1: This is the section in brief.
ai-patthana16.73:5.1_0: Anxieties of the mind and body are produced by consciousness, no producing conditioned by mind, and kept rolling by consciousness.
ai-patthana16.73:5.1_1: This is the section in brief.
